WEBVTT

00:05.839 --> 00:06.340 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Good
evening. I'm Judy Woodruff.

00:06.340 --> 00:08.442 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And I'm Gwen Ifill.

00:08.442 --> 00:13.947 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: On the "NewsHour"
tonight: Did ExxonMobil mislead
the public about its

00:13.947 --> 00:19.586 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
