01:38.699 --> 01:44.604 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The Obama
administration will ask the U.S.
Supreme Court to let it protect

01:44.604 --> 01:50.143 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
