News Asia she expects to be the
de facto leader.

03:38.485 --> 03:40.787 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AUNG SAN SUU KYI, Myanmar
Opposition Leader: In any
democratic country, it's the
leader

03:40.787 --> 03:46.526 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of the winning party who becomes
the leader of the government,
and if this constitution

03:46.526 --> 03:51.631 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
doesn't allow it, then we will
have to make arrangements so
that we can proceed along

03:51.631 --> 03:54.501 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
usual democratic lines.

03:54.501 --> 03:59.005 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Myanmar's military
gave way to an elected regime in
2011, but it retains

03:59.005 --> 04:02.476 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
control of key parts
of the government.

04:02.476 --> 04:07.147 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Russia now says
its ban on flights to Egypt will
last at least the next

04:07.147 --> 04:12.953 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
several months over security
concerns. A Russian airliner
crashed in the Sinai Peninsula
on

04:12.953 --> 04:20.460 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
October 31 after taking off from
Sharm el-Sheikh. All 224 people
on board were killed. U.S.

04:20.460 --> 04:25.031 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and British officials say it's
likely a bomb destroyed the
plane.

04:25.031 --> 04:30.804 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Russian sports
officials are denying
accusations of widespread doping
among track

04:30.804 --> 04:35.075 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and field athletes. The World
Anti-Doping Agency said
yesterday that Moscow has
allowed

04:35.075 --> 04:38.411 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
a state-sponsored drug culture.

04:38.411 --> 04:42.215 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
