athletics federation dismissed
the report and said it

04:42.215 --> 04:45.886 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
shouldn't block Russian athletes
from next year's Olympics.

04:45.886 --> 04:49.556 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
VADIM ZELICHENOK, Acting
President, Russian Athletics
Federation (through translator):

04:49.556 --> 04:54.795 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I am sorry. I want to ask once
again, what are these athletes
guilty of? They have never

04:54.795 --> 04:59.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
had any record of doping
violations. Why should they be
deprived of this opportunity
because

04:59.566 --> 05:02.836 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of the corruption you have
mentioned and which had taken
place several years ago? In any

05:02.836 --> 05:05.839 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
case, currently,
it doesn't exist.

05:05.839 --> 05:10.243 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: President Vladimir
Putin will meet with the head of
the Russian Track Federation

05:10.243 --> 05:13.914 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
tomorrow. Today, Putin's
spokesman said the accusations
appear to be -- quote -- "rather

05:13.914 --> 05:16.016 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
unfounded."

05:16.016 --> 05:21.021 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Federal
prosecutors in New York have
charged three people in a huge
theft

05:21.021 --> 05:26.560 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
