indictment unsealed today said
two

05:26.560 --> 05:32.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Israelis and an American stole
information on more than 80
million households and small

05:32.866 --> 05:37.270 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
business customers at J.P.
Morgan Chase. The crimes were
carried out between 2012 and
this

05:37.270 --> 05:39.639 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
past summer.

05:39.639 --> 05:44.811 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: This was a sluggish
day on Wall Street. The Dow
Jones industrial average gained

05:44.811 --> 05:53.453 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
