Enterprise Institute, ALEC,

12:47.033 --> 12:51.537 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
the American Legislative
Exchange Council, through their
activities with the American

12:51.537 --> 12:56.943 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Petroleum Institute, so
directory and through other
organizations, Exxon has said a
lot

12:56.943 --> 12:59.846 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of things that conflict with the
