been forthcoming about

12:59.846 --> 13:02.215 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
the realities of climate change.

13:02.215 --> 13:05.284 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, let me read
you, Attorney General
Schneiderman, something else
that

13:05.284 --> 13:07.954 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Exxon has been saying where they
