deliberately cherry-picked
statements

13:16.462 --> 13:21.934 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
attributed to various ExxonMobil
employees to wrongly suggest
that conclusions were reached

13:21.934 --> 13:27.407 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
