13:31.210 --> 13:35.381 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ERIC SCHNEIDERMAN: Well, then
they should welcome this
investigation, because, unlike

13:35.381 --> 13:40.119 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
