-- that we decided we had

13:54.634 --> 13:57.603 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to bring this investigation.

13:57.603 --> 14:04.844 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Another area that -- where they
have been active and we're
concerned about is
overestimating

14:04.844 --> 14:11.284 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
